step_data.thought: I've successfully clicked on the CUSTOMERS link in the navigation menu. Looking at the accessibility tree, I can see that clicking on this link has expanded a submenu with several options related to customer management. The submenu contains links to 'All Customers', 'Now Online', 'Login as Customer Log', and 'Customer Groups'. According to the goal, I need to navigate to the Customers section to manage customer accounts, groups, and segments. The 'All Customers' link with ID [363] seems to be the main entry point for managing customer accounts, which aligns with the goal.
